BUSINESS UNDERSTANDING

1) BUSINESS OBJECTIVE   : To Predicting Injury Severity
2) SUCCESS CRITERIA     : Correctly Predicting Injury Severity
3) RESOURCES            : Given dataset, Crash.dat
4) ASSUMPTIONS          : Data is carefully taken and is error-free
5) RISKS                : Wrong prediction of severity of injury
6) REQUIREMENTS         : Clear multiple Regression model
7) DATA MINING GOALS    : Determine indicator and superfluous variables
8) DATA MINING SUCCESS  :
               CRITERIA : Correctly Determining the Vaiables
9) PROJECT PLAN         : Combine the Four Injury Measurement Variables into a Single Variable,
                          Defending your Choice of Combination Function.
